<P><H1 align=center>APPLICATION ENQUIRY - EXTENDED SEARCH - GN210</H1>
<P></P>
<P>In this screen it is possible to define search criteria to find specific 
cases based on the information that you select. You can select individual 
criteria or a mix of criteria depending on your needs.</P>
<P>The criteria is split into four main groups:</P>
<P><STRONG>Organisation, Mortgage Source, Application, Source Of 
Business</STRONG></P>
<P>Select the values you wish to search against from the drop down lists (where 
enabled).</P>
<P>When selecting ‘Indirect’ option from the ‘Direct/Indirect’ field, the 
‘Intermediaries’ button is enabled. Click on this button to enable an 
Intermediary Search facility.</P>
